body:
Hey everyone !

About 3 weeks ago, with the rework hype, I started playing Swain and I LOVED IT. I&#039;m a huge lore fan, my favorite character is Jhin, and we know that he was sent to Noxus at a certain point !  So I went on the wikia and I read as much as possible about Swain, Noxus, Boram Darkwill, and I know a lot of those things aren&#039;t canon anymore, but a theory came to my mind : **Jhin was sent to Noxus to kill Boram Darkwill**

I was not sure at all if Boram Darkwill will be kept canon, but in [Swain Special Interactions](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IaGaqTW6QPQ) we learn that he is still canon !

So here&#039;s my theory :

&gt; - Boram Darkwill decides to invade Ionia;
&gt; - Ionians fight back;
&gt; - Khada Jhin is freed;
&gt; - Swain looses is arm to Irelia;
&gt; - Swain found the demon (Beatrice ?);
&gt; - Noxus is defeated and they head back to Noxus Prime;
&gt; - Swain is ashamed of Darkwill and he wants to take control of Noxus;
&gt; - Jhin is sent to Noxus to kill Boram Darkwill (and 3 other people)
&gt; - Swain then takes the control of Noxus and becomes Noxus Grand General.
&gt; 

I&#039;m pretty sure I can be wrong, but this theory hypes me too much !

Thank you for reading ! :)
